# GG_Break_HillBreak

### Slots: 32 players
### HDR/LDR: both
### Radar/overview: yes
### 3D skybox: yes
### Cubemaps (reflections): yes

This is a remake of gg-break-hillbreak. The map is a huge hill of breakable blocks where you can dig traps and tunnels.

Unfortunately I don't know who original mapper is, but I like his map and that's why I did this remake. I hope there will be more servers with gg-break-hillbreak or gg-break-hillfresh, because I  couldn't find one yesterday.

Also I provide no video today, only screenshots.

iPlayer, URC Team, 2012
